Package: python-flotilla
Architecture: all
Section: python
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}, python-serial (>= 2.6)
Description: python library designed to control Flotilla modules.
 Flotilla is a range of smart, friendly, and affordable modules which you connect
 together to create amazing projects which sense and react to the world around them.
 .
 This is the Python 2 version of the package.

